# Spotless Homes

> Spotless Homes is a family-run Florida house-cleaning company providing trained, insured, and background-checked maid service to Tampa, Saint Petersburg, Clearwater, Jacksonville, Orlando, Fort Lauderdale, Boca Raton, and Fort Myers. Services include recurring residential cleaning, deep cleans, move-in/move-out cleans, Airbnb / short-term rental turnovers, and office cleaning. Average rating {{RATING_LABEL}} across {{RATING_COUNT_SHORT}} reviews.

## Core pages

- [Home](https://www.spotless.homes/): Service overview, areas covered, and instant booking entry point.
- [About](https://www.spotless.homes/about/): Company background, team, and what makes Spotless Homes different.
- [Book a cleaning](https://www.spotless.homes/booking/): Six-step booking flow — pick service type, bedrooms/bathrooms, frequency, date/time, and contact info.
- [Careers](https://www.spotless.homes/careers/): Open positions for cleaners in Florida; apply page is intentionally noindex.

